      Optional<CountryResponse> tryCountry(InetAddress ipAddress) throws IOException, GeoIp2Exception
      Parameters:
      ipAddress - IPv4 or IPv6 address to lookup.
      Returns:
      A Country model for the requested IP address or empty if it is not in the DB.

      GeoIp2Exception - if there is an error looking up the IP
